<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>HEAVENET WIFI</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);
color:white;
text-align:center;
margin:0;
padding:0;
}

.container{
margin-top:80px;
padding:20px;
}

.logo{
font-size:32px;
font-weight:bold;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.subtitle{
opacity:0.8;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.box{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
padding:30px;
border-radius:15px;
max-width:350px;
margin:auto;
backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

input{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-top:10px;
border-radius:8px;
border:none;
font-size:16px;
}

button{
width:100%;
padding:15px;
margin-top:15px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.login{
background:#00e5ff;
}

.buy{
background:#25D366;
}

.planbox{
margin-top:30px;
}

.plan{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
padding:20px;
border-radius:12px;
margin-top:15px;
}

.price{
font-size:22px;
color:#00e5ff;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="logo">
HEAVENET WIFI 🚀
</div>

<div class="subtitle">
Internet comunitario rápido
</div>

<div class="box">

<input type="text" placeholder="Ingresa tu clave o voucher">

<button class="login">
Acceder con clave
</button>

<button class="buy" onclick="window.location.href='https://heavenetwork.github.io/heavennetwork-wifi/planes.html'">
Comprar plan
</button>

</div>

<div class="planbox">

<div class="plan">
<h3>1 Día</h3>
<div class="price">$20 MXN</div>
</div>

<div class="plan">
<h3>7 Días</h3>
<div class="price">$60 MXN</div>
</div>

<div class="plan">
<h3>1 Mes</h3>
<div class="price">$100 MXN</div>
<p>Promoción apertura de zona</p>
<p>Después de 6 meses: $200 MXN</p>
<p>Incluye plataformas de streaming 📺</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
